QuestData.Title: Growing Wood
QuestData.Description:
We got the lumber mill good an' built, but we be needin' more wood!
The Rangari tol' me there's botani usin' some kinda sap to grow ancients fast as you like.
Get yer hands on some o' that sap and I betcha I can put it work.
What? Oh, Glyza here? Found 'er crashed here and she knows a thing or two about lumberjackin'. I'll take her back to the outpost later.
I'll meet ya inside Tangleheart if I can find it.
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect $1oa Ancient Growth Sap from botani or ancients.
QuestData.RewardText: Sap? Who called me a sap?! Oh...
